
# tap repositories and their packages

## caskroom/cask
tap caskroom/cask
install brew-cask
cask install atom
cask install google-chrome
cask install google-japanese-ime
cask install iterm2
cask install skitch

## motemen/ghq
tap motemen/ghq
install ghq

## peco/peco
tap peco/peco
install peco

## rcmdnk/file
tap rcmdnk/file
install brew-file

